  <summary date="2021-08-30T16:24:29Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Natural Disaster and Emergency Ballot Act of 2020

This bill revises and establishes voting procedures for federal elections. For example, states must establish plans to enable voting during an emergency and must take certain actions to facilitate early voting and absentee voting.</summary>
